                    </state>
                    <note type="corrigenda">GEDSH Map II displays the location too far to the south, east of <placeName ref="http://syriaca.org/place/91">Ḥama</placeName> rather than west of <placeName ref="http://syriaca.org/place/18">Aleppo</placeName>.</note>
                    <note type="corrigenda">In Dolabani's translation of Barsoum's description <quote xml:lang="syr-Syrj">ܕܐܶܦܶܣܘܣ</quote> should read <quote xml:lang="syr-Syrj">ܕܶܐܦܶܣܘܣ</quote>.</note>
